<p>The map shows the percentage of statin prescription items in two classes of branded statins, at PCT level. NICE guidelines say that the generic Simvastatin should be a default option for patients. Wherever the percentage of branded items is high, it represents potential to make big savings by switching. Those savings could be used to help more patients.</p>
